                            <comment id="15252485" author="thobbs" created="Thu, 21 Apr 2016 19:12:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch is pretty straightfoward.  There were still a few uses of &lt;tt&gt;getNonSystemKeyspaces()&lt;/tt&gt; that made sense with the current behavior, so I simply added a new &lt;tt&gt;getNonLocalStrategyKeyspaces()&lt;/tt&gt; method and switched most users over to that.&lt;/p&gt;

